data.description: Well maintained four bedroom and two bath home on a large corner lot with sprinkler system. Swimming pool with covered patio makes great space for entertaining but still plenty of room for animals to roam if needed.  Large living area with vaulted ceilings opens up to kitchen with large windows looking over beautiful pool.  Home also has split bedrooms, Master bedroom and bath are big and spacious.  Home is very well maintained, close to schools with easy access to tollway if needed.  This home has side 2 car garage with plenty of parking if needed.
